### Task B: Build Pre-Auth Document Generator

**Objective:** Create a function that takes NEXUS output + patient info and generates a TPA-ready pre-authorization document.

**Input:**
```typescript
interface PreAuthInput {
  // From NEXUS
  diagnosis: string;
  probability: number;
  clinical_reasoning: string;
  severity_indicators: {
    pheno_intensity: number;
    urgency_quotient: number;
    deterioration_velocity: number;
  };
  evidence_anchors: Array<{finding: string; strength: number}>;
  
