### Task C: Build ICD Code Suggester

**Objective:** Auto-suggest ICD codes from NEXUS diagnosis output.

```typescript
function suggestICDCodes(nexusDiagnosis: string, icdDatabase: ICDDatabase): ICDSuggestion[] {
  // 1. Fuzzy match diagnosis against condition names + aliases
  const matches = icdDatabase.conditions.filter(c => 
    fuzzyMatch(nexusDiagnosis, c.condition_name) ||
    c.common_aliases.some(a => fuzzyMatch(nexusDiagnosis, a)) ||
    c.hinglish_terms.some(h => fuzzyMatch(nexusDiagnosis, h))
  );
  
  // 2. Rank by match confidence
  const ranked = matches.map(m => ({
    condition: m,
    confidence: calculateMatchConfidence(nexusDiagnosis, m)
  })).sort((a, b) => b.confidence - a.confidence);
  
  // 3. Return top 3 suggestions with codes
  return ranked.slice(0, 3).map(r => ({
    condition_name: r.condition.condition_name,
    confidence: r.confidence,
    primary_code: r.condition.icd_codes.primary,
    variants: r.condition.icd_codes.specific_variants,
    associated_codes: r.condition.commonly_associated_codes
  }));
}
```

